description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

 

The duo catch up on Leisha's trip to Paris and how Kate hurt herself. They then answer questions and share thoughts on quotes to live by, moving in with a friend, rudest things our pets have done, and if you should meet your biological father or start your dream career.

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod
